Earlyn CARRIER, Jr. v. DEBARGE’S COLLEGE JUNCTION. No. 96-C-0472. Supreme Court of Louisiana. April 8, 1996.

Prior report: LaApp., — So.2d-.

In re Debarge’s College Junction;—Defendant(s); applying for writ of certiorari and/or review; Office of Workers’ Compensation, Dist. 2, No. 93-05494; to the Court of Appeal, Third Circuit, No. CA95 0018.
